name: Qr02_Campanha_FimdeAno2021_Trata_Nao_Importune
queryText:
SELECT
	A.CPF_CNPJ,
	1 AS NAO_IMPORTUNE
FROM Tb_Campanha_FimdeAno2021_Base A
INNER JOIN TB_BASE_NAO_IMPORTUNE N ON ISNULL(CONCAT(A.DDD_TEL_01, A.TEL_01), '00000000000') = LTRIM(RTRIM(N.TELEFONE))
UNION
